      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p>Angulotls make use of a unique effect called “wet.” While wet, an angulotl doesn’t provoke opportunity attacks by moving. At the same time, any non-angulotl who is wet and ends their turn with none of their movement remaining slips and falls prone. Several angulotl abilities can impose this effect, but a creature in an encounter featuring angulotls can also become wet by entering water, as the Director determines.</p>",
          "chat": ""
        },
